dcterms:description: The CQ dataset is a subset of the CQ500 dataset, consisting of 63 midline shift subjects and the same number of healthy subjects. 59% of the subjects have a significant midline shift (≥ 5mm) and the mean MLS is 7.59 ± 5.16mm.
dcterms:title: CQ dataset

dcterms:description: The inhouse dataset consists of 203 CT series which have different degrees of midline shift caused by cerebral hemorrhage. 78% of the subjects have a significant midline shift (≥ 5mm) and the mean MLS is 9.04 ± 5.54mm.
dcterms:title: Inhouse dataset
